  "keyFeatures": [
    "Declarative signatures to define LM input/output behavior without prompt engineering",
    "Composable modules (Predict, ChainOfThought, ReAct, ProgramOfThought) for building AI pipelines",
    "Automatic prompt optimization with MIPROv2, GEPA, BootstrapFewShot, and other optimizers",
    "Weight fine-tuning via BootstrapFinetune for LM adaptation",
    "Multi-LM provider support via LiteLLM (OpenAI, Anthropic, Gemini, local models, and more)",
    "Streaming, async, and caching support for production deployments",
    "Built-in evaluation framework with metrics like SemanticF1",
    "MCP (Model Context Protocol) tool integration",
    "Modular agent architectures with ReAct and tool use"
  ],
